#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:1
msgid "回测引擎与性能"
msgstr "Backtesting Engine and Performance"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:3
msgid ""
"本章从**使用与结果**角度说明 qteasy 的回测引擎如何工作，以及**性能与向量化**"
"的实现方式，便于用户理解回测速度与正确性的来源。更底层的架构说明见《架构与设"
"计》中的 [回测引擎与性能（设计视角）](../design/07-backtest-engine-and-"
"performance.md)。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter explains how qteasy’s backtesting engine works from the "
"perspective of **usage and results**, and how **performance and "
"vectorization** are implemented, helping users understand where backtest "
"speed and correctness come from. For a lower-level architectural "
"explanation, see [Backtesting Engine and Performance (Design Perspective)]"
"(../design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md) in “Architecture and "
"Design”."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:5
msgid "1. 回测引擎概览"
msgstr "1. Backtesting Engine Overview"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:7
#, python-format
msgid ""
"回测入口与流程已在 [回测概览](1.%20overview.md) 与 [如何运行回测]"
"(2.%20run_backtest.md) 中说明：通过 `qt.run(op, mode=1, ...)` 进入回测模式，"
"内部按 **group_timing_table** 的每个时间步运行策略、解析信号并模拟成交。"
msgstr ""
"The backtest entry point and workflow have been described in [Backtest "
"Overview](1.%20overview.md) and [How to Run a Backtest]"
"(2.%20run_backtest.md): enter backtest mode via `qt.run(op, mode=1, ...)`, "
"and internally, at each time step in **group_timing_table**, run the "
"strategy, parse signals, and simulate executions."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:9
msgid ""
"与“逐 bar 事件驱动”或“全时间轴一次性矩阵运算”不同，qteasy 采用 **时间维顺序"
"步进、单步内标的维向量化** 的方式："
msgstr ""
"Unlike “bar-by-bar event-driven” or “one-shot matrix operations over the "
"full timeline,” qteasy uses **time-dimension sequential stepping with "
"instrument-dimension vectorization within each step**:"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:11
msgid ""
"**时间维**：按真实交易节奏顺序执行每个时间步，以正确维护现金、持仓、交割队列"
"（如 T+1）等状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Time dimension**: Execute each time step in real trading cadence order to "
"correctly maintain states such as cash, positions, and the settlement queue "
"(e.g., T+1)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:12
msgid ""
"**标的维**：在每个时间步内，对资产池中所有标的的买卖量、费用、持仓更新等做 "
"**向量化计算**（NumPy 数组 + Numba 加速），单步效率高。"
msgstr ""
"**Instrument dimension**: Within each time step, perform **vectorized "
"computations** (NumPy arrays + Numba acceleration) for all instruments in "
"the asset pool—buy/sell volumes, fees, position updates, etc.—achieving "
"high per-step efficiency."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:14
msgid ""
"这样既保证了与实盘一致的状态与规则，又避免了纯事件驱动下的逐笔循环带来的性能"
"损失。"
msgstr ""
"This both ensures states and rules consistent with live trading, and avoids "
"the performance loss caused by per-tick loops under a purely event-driven "
"approach."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:16
msgid "2. 性能与向量化"
msgstr "2. Performance and Vectorization"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:18
msgid "2.1 核心计算加速"
msgstr "2.1 Core Computation Acceleration"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:20
msgid ""
"回测与交易结果计算中的以下核心函数均使用 **Numba JIT**（`@njit(nogil=True, "
"cache=True)`）加速："
msgstr ""
"The following core functions in backtesting and trade-result calculation "
"are all accelerated with **Numba JIT** (`@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`):"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:22
msgid "**backtest_step**：单步内对整批标的计算买卖量、费用、持仓与交割更新。"
msgstr ""
"**backtest_step**: Within a single step, compute buy/sell volumes, fees, "
"positions, and settlement updates for the whole batch of instruments."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:23
msgid "**calculate_trade_results**：交易结果与资金变动计算。"
msgstr "**calculate_trade_results**: Trade results and cash-flow calculation."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:24
msgid ""
"**backtest_batch_steps**：在 Numba 内按时间步循环调用 `backtest_step`，完成"
"整段回测。"
msgstr ""
"**backtest_batch_steps**: Loop over time steps inside Numba and call "
"`backtest_step` to complete the entire backtest segment."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:25
msgid ""
"**backtest_flash_steps**：优化模式下使用，仅保留最终资金与持仓以节省内存，同"
"样在 Numba 内完成批量步进。"
msgstr ""
"**backtest_flash_steps**: Used only in optimization mode; keeps only the "
"final cash and positions to save memory, and likewise completes batch "
"stepping within Numba."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:27
msgid ""
"信号混合（如多策略合并）在 `blender` 模块中部分算子也使用 `@njit` 加速。因"
"此，回测主体是 **向量化 + Numba** 实现的，而非纯 Python 循环。"
msgstr ""
"Signal mixing (e.g., merging multiple strategies) also uses `@njit` "
"acceleration for some operators in the `blender` module. Therefore, the "
"main backtesting engine is implemented with **vectorization + Numba**, "
"rather than pure Python loops."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:29
msgid "2.2 时间维顺序与标的维向量化"
msgstr ""
"2.2 Time-Dimension Ordering and Vectorization Along the Instrument Dimension"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "维度"
msgstr "Dimension"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "做法说明"
msgstr "Approach Overview"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "时间维"
msgstr "Time Dimension"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "顺序步进，以正确维护 T+1、交割周期、MOQ 等状态，与实盘一致。"
msgstr ""
"Step forward sequentially to correctly maintain states such as T+1, "
"settlement cycles, MOQ, etc., consistent with live trading."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "标的维"
msgstr "Instrument Dimension"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid ""
"单步内对所有标的做数组运算（如 `op_signal`、`own_amounts` 等为 1D 数组），实"
"现向量化。"
msgstr ""
"Perform array operations for all instruments within a single step (e.g., "
"`op_signal`, `own_amounts`, etc. are 1D arrays) to achieve vectorization."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "优化模式"
msgstr "Optimization Mode"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid ""
"多组参数通过多进程并行回测；每组内部使用 `backtest_flash_steps` 等高效路径，"
"减少内存与计算。"
msgstr ""
"Multiple parameter sets are backtested in parallel via multiprocessing; "
"within each set, efficient paths such as `backtest_flash_steps` are used to "
"reduce memory and computation."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:37
msgid ""
"首次运行或参数变化时，Numba 会编译相关函数，可能带来一次性的启动延迟；后续同"
"类型回测会复用缓存，速度更快。"
msgstr ""
"On the first run or when parameters change, Numba compiles the relevant "
"functions, which may introduce a one-time startup delay; subsequent "
"backtests of the same type will reuse the cache and run faster."

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:39
msgid "2.3 与 VectorBT 的简要对比"
msgstr "2.3 Brief comparison with VectorBT"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "对比项"
msgstr "Comparison item"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "qteasy"
msgstr "qteasy"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "VectorBT"
msgstr "VectorBT"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "顺序步进，每步内向量化"
msgstr "Step forward sequentially, vectorized within each step"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "全时间轴一次性矩阵运算，无显式时间循环"
msgstr ""
"One-shot matrix operations over the full timeline, with no explicit time "
"loop"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "状态与约束"
msgstr "States and constraints"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "显式维护 T+1、交割、MOQ 等，贴近实盘"
msgstr ""
"Explicitly maintains T+1, settlement, MOQ, etc., closely matching live "
"trading"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "多为简化资金曲线，不强调交割/MOQ"
msgstr "Mostly simplified equity curves; does not emphasize settlement/MOQ"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "适用场景"
msgstr "Applicable scenarios"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "需要正确模拟 A 股规则、多策略合并、精细成本与交割时"
msgstr ""
"When you need to accurately simulate A-share rules, merge multiple "
"strategies, and model detailed costs and settlement"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md
msgid "海量参数组合快速筛选、研究向回测"
msgstr ""
"Rapid screening of massive parameter combinations; research-oriented "
"backtesting"

#: ../../source/back_testing/6. backtest_engine_and_performance.md:47
msgid ""
"qteasy 在保证**状态正确性与规则可配置**的前提下，通过时间维顺序 + 标的维向量"
"化 + Numba 单步，兼顾速度；多组参数优化则通过多进程并行弥补“单次不能全矩阵广"
"播”的差异。"
msgstr ""
"On the premise of ensuring **state correctness and configurable rules**, "
"qteasy balances speed through time-axis sequencing + instrument-axis "
"vectorization + Numba single-step execution; multi-parameter optimization, "
"meanwhile, makes up for the difference of “not being able to broadcast the "
"full matrix in a single run” via multiprocessing parallelism."

